Package: build-log-analyzer
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0
Description: GTK4 sbuild and pbuilder log analyzer with error highlighting
 build-log-analyzer parses and displays sbuild and pbuilder build logs
 in a GTK4 interface. It highlights errors, warnings, and provides
 structured views of Debian package build output.
